{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"43148a069c","title":"中共中央关于计算贪污款物原则的指示","origin":"根据文件的翻印件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2e5040d3f5","index":0,"year":1952,"month":3,"day":15,"articleId":"43148a069c"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"1fb4e2bbd8","type":"title","text":"中共中央关于计算贪污款物原则的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"43148a069c"},{"id":"dc04d6369a","type":"appellation","text":"西北局并告各中央局，转分局、省市区党委、地委；各大军区党委转各级军区党委；志愿军党委转兵团、军、师党委：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"43148a069c"},{"id":"1ba74ab99f","type":"paragraph","text":"三月十二日电悉。贪污分子贪污之款物，一般以按当时货币实数实价计算为原则，不折算现价，惟：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"43148a069c"},{"id":"72d92c18db","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）贪污情节严重恶劣者；","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"43148a069c"},{"id":"233cc0eff9","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）一贯贪污为数较大者；","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"43148a069c"},{"id":"535436dbd6","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）将贪污款物投资经营工商业或采用其他方法（如放债）取利或购置不动产者，均应将当时贪污款物按照折实单位（无折实单位规定者可按米价），折成现时币值数目计算。其他有关退赃办法，政务院即将有具体规定发表。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"43148a069c"},{"id":"03b7556a86","type":"paragraph","text":" 中 央三月十五日","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"43148a069c"}],"page":{"id":"b6e50890fb","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"43148a069c","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}